---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects — Emery Silberman">
	<section class="container my-xl">
		<h1>Selected Projects</h1>
		<p class="lead mt-lg">A range of technical solutions at the intersection of agriculture, remote sensing, and software engineering.</p>

		<div class="projects-grid mt-xl">
			<div class="card project-card">
				<div class="tag">Mobile App</div>
				<h3>GOES Viewer</h3>
				<p>A mobile application for real-time viewing and sharing of NOAA satellite imagery. Built to provide farmers and meteorologists with instant access to high-resolution weather data.</p>
				<div class="links mt-lg">
					<a href="https://apps.apple.com" target="_blank" class="block-link">App Store &rarr;</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card project-card">
				<div class="tag">Open Source</div>
				<h3>Immibridge</h3>
				<p>An open-source synchronization tool for Apple Photo libraries and Immich. Solves the gap in self-hosted photo management for Mac users.</p>
				<div class="links mt-lg">
					<a href="https://github.com/emerysilberman" target="_blank" class="block-link">GitHub &rarr;</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card project-card">
				<div class="tag">Ag-Tech</div>
				<h3>Smart Farm Integration</h3>
				<p>At UC Merced, I lead the software engineering for the experimental smart farm, integrating diverse sensor networks with cloud-based visualization tools.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card project-card">
				<div class="tag">Enterprise</div>
				<h3>Bowles Management Suite</h3>
				<p>A custom ecosystem of Flutter applications used to manage 11,000 acres. Features include real-time labor tracking, harvest logistics, and irrigation management.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.lead {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		max-width: 60ch;
	}
	.projects-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: var(--space-lg);
	}
	.project-card {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}
	.project-card h3 {
		margin: var(--space-sm) 0;
	}
	.project-card p {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		flex-grow: 1;
	}
	.tag {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-green-soft);
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}
	.block-link {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-green-primary);
	}
</style>
